<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>57</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Naendea Msalaba,
 Ni mnyonge na mpofu,
 Yapitayo naacha,
 Nipone Msalabani.

[V2]
 Nakutumaini tu,
 Ewe Mwana wa Mungu;
 Nainamia kwako;
 Niponye, mponya wangu.

[V3]
 Nakulilia sana:
 Nalemewa na dhambi;
 Pole Yesu asema;
 'Nitazifuta zote'.

[V4]
 Natoa vyote kwako,
 Nafasi nazo nguvu,
 Roho yangu na mwili,
 Viwe vyako milele.

[V5]
 Kwa damu yake sasa,
 Nimegeuka roho,
 Nikaziacha tama
 Nimfuate Yesu tu.

[V6]
 Yesu yuaja tena!
 Nimepevuka kwake,
 Kila chembe kamili;
 Msifuni yeye mponya!</lyrics>
<title>Naendea Msalaba TZR57</title>
</song>